\nW_{S}=\\frac{1/4}{3}\\left[0.8414709848078965+5.2858615106576068+1.3299933154720726+0.45464871341284085\\right]\\\\\n=\\frac{1}{12}\\left[7.91197452435041675\\right]\\approx 0.6593312103625347.\n\\end{aligned}\n$$\n\n使用 $W_{ref}=0.65932991$，绝对误差为\n$$\nE_{T}=|W_{T}-W_{ref}|=|0.6586304711277017-0.65932991|\\approx 6.994388722983\\times 10^{-4},\n$$\n$$\nE_{S}=|W_{S}-W_{ref}|=|0.6593312103625347-0.65932991|\\approx 1.3003625347\\times 10^{-6}.\n$$\n因此，所求的绝对差为\n$$\n|E_{T}-E_{S}|\\approx 6.981385097637\\times 10^{-4}.\n$$\n四舍五入到三位有效数字，结果为\n$$\n6.98\\times 10^{-4}.\n$$",
